'''Tawsit''' ([[asget]]: ''tiwsitin'') d [[Adras amessarti]] n unagi neɣ n unadi deg [[tsertut tusnant n telmas|tasartut tusnant n telmas]] yeɣɣaren deg waɛas n [[Amuddir|imuddiren]] yettemcabin deg talɣa d uẓaṛ

== Assissen ==


Akk [[talmest|tilmas]] n [[Amuddir|imuddiren]] ([[aɣersiw]], [[tuga]], [[imɣan]], [[agersal|igersalen]]…) ttwaqqnen ar yiwet n tewsit, ɣef uguni n [[assaɣ usnan|ussaɣ usnan]] yettwassissenen sɣur [[Carl von Linné]].


Yal talmest tezmer at sɛu aṭas [[adu-talmest|adu-tilmas]] : [[tuggta (taḥcict)|tuggtiwin]] neɣ [[talɣa (taḥcict)|talɣiwin]] <br />
S umedya, [[awerɣil amenkad]] (isem alatini : ''Aptenodytes forsteri'') d [[awerɣil ageldan|uwerɣil ageldan]] (''Aptenodytes patagonica'') llan sin yidsen deg ṣṣenf ''Aptenodytes'', n [[tawacult (tasnudert)|twacult]] n sapiens'[[awerɣil|iwerɣilen]].

Kra n tugrinin, am [[tasnagersal]], steɛṛefen abeṭṭu arqaq n ṣṣenf ar '''Adu-telmas, Tigezmi , Adu-tigezmi '''.

Tawsit talsant semman-as [[Homo]].
